é en 1219, à Towcester, Northamptonshire, Angleterre, son père, Walter de Pateshulle, avait 28 ans et sa mère, Margaret Argentine, avait 11216 ans. Il a épousé Margery Braybrook en 1236, à Towcester, Northamptonshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils. Sa profession de son indiquée est sherriff of buckinghamshire à Buckinghamshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il est décédé le 1 avril 1274, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 55 ans."},"de":{"1219–1 April 1274":"1219–1. April 1274","1219–1274":"1219–1274","1224–Female":"1224–Verstorben","1240–1290":"1240–1290","1192–1232":"1192–1232","1203–1232":"1203–1232","1 April 1274":"1. April 1274","Aft 1232":"nach 1232","1274":"1274","1240":"1240","before 1219":"vor 1219","1192":"1192","1290":"1290","Abt 1240":"um 1240","1259":"1259","1236":"1236","1203":"1203","1224":"1224","1232":"1232","1219":"1219","20 August 1232":"20. August 1232","Towcester, Northamptonshire, England":"Towcester, Northamptonshire, England","England":"England, United Kingdom","Pattishall, Northamptonshire, England":"Pattishall, Northamptonshire, England","lifeSummary":"Als Simon de Pateshulle 1219 in Towcester, Northamptonshire, England geboren wurde, war sein Vater Walter de Pateshulle 28 und seine Mutter Margaret Argentine 11216. Er hat 1236 in Towcester, Northamptonshire, England, United Kingdom Margery Braybrook geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Sohn. sein Beruf ist als sherriff of buckinghamshire in Buckinghamshire, England, United Kingdom aufgeführt. Er starb am 1. April 1274 im Alter von 55 Jahren in seinem Geburtsort."},"ht":{"1219–1 April 1274":"1219–1 April 1274","1219–1274":"1219–1274","1224–Female":"1224–Desede","1240–1290":"1240–1290","1192–1232":"1192–1232","1203–1232":"1203–1232","1 April 1274":"1 April 1274","Aft 1232":"after 1232","1274":"1274","1240":"1240","before 1219":"before 1219","1192":"1192","1290":"1290","Abt 1240":"about 1240","1259":"1259","1236":"1236","1203":"1203","1224":"1224","1232":"1232","1219":"1219","20 